import React from 'react';
import {Container,Row,Col,Image,Button,Dropdown} from 'react-bootstrap';
import {useHistory}  from "react-router-dom";
import './header.scss';

const header = ()=>{
    let history = useHistory();
        return (
           <Container fluid>
                <Row className = {"header"}>
                    <Col className={"logo"}>TaraTari</Col>
                    <Col className>
                        <Dropdown>
                            <Dropdown.Toggle variant="success" id="dropdown-basic">
                                Select Items
                            </Dropdown.Toggle>
                            <Dropdown.Menu>
                                <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-1">Action</Dropdown.Item>
                                <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-2">Another action</Dropdown.Item>
                                <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">Something else</Dropdown.Item>
                            </Dropdown.Menu>
                        </Dropdown>
                    </Col>
                    <Col className>
                        <Dropdown>
                            <Dropdown.Toggle variant="success" id="dropdown-basic">
                                Select Location
                            </Dropdown.Toggle>
                            <Dropdown.Menu>
                                <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-1">Action</Dropdown.Item>
                                <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-2">Another action</Dropdown.Item>
                                <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">Something else</Dropdown.Item>
                            </Dropdown.Menu>
                        </Dropdown>
                    </Col>
                    <Col>
                        <Image className = {"search-icon"} alt='' src={require("../assets/search.png")}/>
                    </Col>
                    <Col>
                        <Button onClick = {()=>{history.push('/Category')}} className={"sell-button"}  >SELL</Button>
                    </Col>
                </Row> 
            </Container>

    );
};

export default header;
